.TH LOOTSHEET-QUEST-COLLECT 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-quest-collect \\- Collect cash against an earned quest reward
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet quest collect [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet quest collect --id ID --amount AMOUNT --date YYYY-MM-DD [--description TEXT]

Examples:
  lootsheet quest collect --id quest-123 --amount 10GP --date 2026-03-15
  lootsheet quest collect --id quest-123 --amount 5GP --date 2026-03-16 --description "Second pouch from the mayor"
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--amount=string
payment amount (required) (default: )
.TP
--date=string
payment date in YYYY-MM-DD (required) (default: )
.TP
--description=string
optional description (default: )
.TP
-h, --help
help for collect
.TP
--id=string
quest ID (required) (default: )
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-quest(1)
